<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">This subchapter may be cited as the “National Labor Relations Act”.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id5a230aa7-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c">(<ref href="/us/act/1935-07-05/ch372/s17">July 5, 1935, ch. 372, § 17</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/act/1947-06-23/ch120">June 23, 1947, ch. 120</ref>, title I, § 101, <ref href="/us/stat/61/152">61 Stat. 152</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
