<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="id5a230aaa-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">For effective date of amendment by act <date date="1947-06-23">June 23, 1947</date>, see section 104 of act <date date="1947-06-23">June 23, 1947</date>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t29/s151">section 151 of this title</ref>.</p>
